== 认证 ==
'''纽约摄影学院'''经[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Distance_Education_Training_Council 国家远程教育培训理事会（Distance Education Training Council）]认证，可以提供远程教育培训<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.detc.org/school_details.php?id=256 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214170427/http://www.detc.org/school_details.php?id=256 |archive-date=2012-02-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。此外，由于学院位于[[纽约|纽约]]，同时也由纽约州教育部(New York State Department of Education)许可。

[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Better_Business_Bureau 商业改进局（Better Business Bureau）] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Better_Business_Bureau |date=20210422071706 }}将纽约摄影学院评为A级<ref>http://www.bbb.org/new-york-city/business-reviews/photography-schools/new-york-institute-of-photography-in-new-york-ny-883/ {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbb.org/new-york-city/business-reviews/photography-schools/new-york-institute-of-photography-in-new-york-ny-883/ |date=20121104150136 }} 商业改进局</ref>。

